sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Orchestrator
    participant Critic as CriticAgent
    participant FS as Run Workspace

    Orchestrator->>Critic: critique(figure.svg, plan, sections)
    Critic-->>Orchestrator: CritiqueReport
    Orchestrator->>FS: write critique.json
    alt Score >= threshold
        Orchestrator-->>FS: mark figure accepted
    else Score < threshold
        Orchestrator-->>FS: mark figure for regeneration
    end
